reviewText:
I love Renee Zellweger!

I wish I could kiss her!

The only movie I didn't like was BRIDGET JONE'S DIARY.

But CHICAGO and COLD HARBOR are fantastic.

Her versatility and talent are amazing!

I used to act in community theatre productions, so I know what I'm talking about when I say she is EXTREMELY gifted, and REALLY worked long and hard to attain her position.

RENEE ZELLWEGER IS ANOTHER STAR ---  SHE ALSO ACTED IN A MOVIE WITH NICOLE KIDMAN & JUDE LAW FILMED  IN TWO TOWNS WITHIN 45MIN DRIVE OR OPPOSITE SIDES OF MY CURRENT HOMETOWN.  I WAS WORKING IN ONE OF THOSE TOWNS & HAD CHANCE TO BE IN THE MOVIE (WOULD HAVE HAD TO QUIT MY JOB)

I THINK THERE ARE SO MANY STARS THAT HAVE A 3 OR 4 YEAR POPULARITY STREAK.....BUT THEN BECOME YESTERDAYS NEWS
(PERHAPS BECAUSE OF SCRIPTS OR STARS WANT A BREAK  OR  THEY DEMAND HIGHER SALARY OR FILM GROSS)----
I bought this film collection because my sister asked me to. She said it was great!
Good old fashioned kind of movies. Fun to watch and wholesome.
Redeived so quickly! Great dvd!

I LOVE THESE MOVIES.. She is one of my favorite actresses and i bought this set for Bridgit Jones and Chicago i alreaey had the other movie..but this is a must have for any fan..i love the convience of having all of these in one place instead of searching through my entire collection of dvds for the individual movies
Renee is so great in this movie.  Like it because it happens in Minnesota!
All I wanted was New In Town - the other movies are not good.
good movies
great collection, and a great price
Really love all the movies and was tired of not find Bridget Jone's Diary on TV and Cold Mountain. This looks like one DVD case but has 4 separate movies nice put in the case.
I love Renee Zellweger and with this, I got 4 of her best movies.  They are great and arrived quickly and were packaged great.  Would buy again...!!!
Worth every cent. And three of the four movies have commentary (Cold Mountain doesn't).
She is the best of the best, and I wish she'd make more movies. Well worth the price.
I love these movies. I will watch them over and over again.

Three of Her best Films here.
Great deal for the Price.

This four movie set is a bargain.  You'll see Renee's professionalism on display in a number of roles.  Watching all the movies, one after the other, reinforces your appreciation of this actresses dedication to her craft.

Believe it or not I may be one of the only women my age that had not watched or read Bridget Jones Diary. Came across the movie one day on TNT and only caught the tail end. Bought it to get the full picture. The additional movies were a bonus.
Especially in her role as Bridget Jones!  The main reason I got this was for that movie but figured it was a bonue with her other flicks.
FIRST OF ALL, YOU REALLY GET 4 DVD'S AND NOT 2 TWO-SIDED DVD'S THIS IS A GREAT BUY WITH FANTASTIC MOVIES. RENEE ZELLWEGER AT HER BEST IN 4 DVD'S!!! FANTASTIC DEAL! BUY IT, YOU WON'T REGRET IT.
Not much to say -- it is what it says it is, and my wife loves them all!  Great film selections.
Great movie
I love Renee's movies! These four I really liked so it was money well spent.
Super movies!
work great
Love her.
Great buy!  Love Renee!
Who doesn't love a good Chick flick with Renee? I love how she just puts herself out there.
Good films.  4 disks.  Subtitles, etc.
This lady can really make me laugh,lots of war of north and south,heartbreaking,funny and very human movies,4 disc with lots to choose from  from Renee Zellweger !
Great selections
